lead_paragraph: Interpol has for two weeks been circulating a call for the arrest of Julian Assange on sex crimes charges.
snippet: Interpol has for two weeks been circulating a call for the arrest of Julian Assange on sex crimes charges.

headline.main: Interpol Called for Arrest of WikiLeaks Founder
headline.seo: Interpol Announces Call for Arrest of WikiLeaks Founder
headline.print_headline: Interpol Calls for WikiLeaks Founder’s Arrest in Connection With Swedish Cases

byline.original: By JOHN F. BURNS and ALAN COWELL
byline.contributor: John F. Burns reported from London, and Alan Cowell from Paris. Ravi Somaiya contributed reporting from London, and Verne G. Kopytoff from San Francisco.
